    "attributes": {
        "action": "Offer grants for accommodation owners to install  EV charging facilities.",
        "additional_details": "Evidence of the climate crisis is increasingly becoming apparent. This Government has prior to COP26 set targets for the UK to reduce carbon emissions by enabling the use of electric vehicles. A grant for accommodation owners would be good value approach for helping the UK Government achieve the targets it has set out for itself.",
        "background": "When travelling in the UK using an Electric Vehicle (EV) it would be desirable to charge the car at any destination accommodation. The present cost of installation is prohibitive for hosts, so grants should be available to help the UK meet its carbon reduction target.",
